data.description: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled four-bedroom, three-and-a-half-bath California-style home in the heart of Bowie, Maryland. The location is perfect- close to local highways and shopping malls. The top-to-bottom updates of this home feels both cozy and luxurious!! The entire home boasts stunning hardwood flooring , and recessed lighting all throughout. You will love all the solid tasteful finishes throughout, most new! The living room is flooded with natural light and flows into the spacious dining room. The family room features a beautiful double sided fireplace and access to a large composite deck with a huge modern pool. The kitchen has a stunning open island with quartz counters, custom cabinetry, stainless appliances, a five-burner electric cooktop with a microwave, and much more. The main-level primary bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, and bright windows. The other three bedrooms offer ample closet space and lighting as well. The party room/mother in law suit is an empty canvas ready for you to build anything you desire, 2 story ceiling!! Property has 2 attached and 3 detached garages! Huge driveway and  2 new hvacs in the house!
